title: Jamie O'Hara parties with bikini clad babes before hitting strip club with Calum Best
text:
INSTAGRAM BROMANCE: Cal and Jamie hit the town together 
Joined by new mate Calum Best, the footy-ace hit up swanky Paper nightclub in Soho straight after his stint on CBBBOTS. 
Dressed in his trademark blue velvet jacket and dark trousers, the star looked dapper as ever as he partied up a storm surrounded by bikini clad dancers and more booze than we would know what to do with. 
In fact, even Jamie seemed surprised by the amount of bottles arriving to the V.I.P area of the club. 
SNAPCHAT RACY: Jamie filmed bikini clad dancers in Paper club The best bits from CBB 2017 Monday, 30th January 2017 Are you watching CBB 2017? Take a look at the best bits here! 1 / 111 
Taking to Snapchat the star filmed a human conveyor belt of scantily dressed girls filling past with luxury champagne complete with fireworks for added effect. 
Though seemingly unimpressed he simply captioned the upload "stupid." 
But that didn't mean he wasn't in the partying mood. 
SNAPCHAT FREE MAN: Jamie seems to be enjoying life outside of CBB 
In fact, despite leaving the hotspot just after 3.15am he found a new hangout minutes later. 
And we're not too sure how potential new girlfriend Bianca Gascoigne is going to react. 
Keeping the bromance alive, Jamie and Calum were seen entering Leicester Square strip joint Platinum Lace. Bianca Gascoigne weight loss How Bianca Gascoigne lost 19lbs in six weeks to look sexy for CBB! 1 / 23 Bianca Gascoigne before and after the weight loss 
DS LOOK BUT DON'T TOUCH: Calum and Jamie enter the strip club 
Taking to Instagram earlier in the night, Jamie made no secret of his plans telling the camera: "So we are out. 
"Straight out with my boy. We are going straight out on the town we are going to f***ing live it up for a few nights." 
Awkwardly, as Jamie ogled at the dancers Bianca was locked in a bitter war of words with Kim Woodburn over her new crush. 
In scenes aired on Big Brother's late night live stream show, the reality TV babe was heard referring to Jamie as "her man" as the How Clean Is Your House star let rip. Related articles
